$interpreted: Miranda: You again...have you seen Miss Fatima?
Miranda: I saw her go into the mountains alone and I wanted to see where she was going, but I lost her right away...
Panther Thug: Oh, shut it! Who do you think you are, taking our Holy Talisman? You tryin' to disrespect us?
Miranda: Fatima and the matriarch said I was a guest. Why are you still harrassing me?
Panther Mafioso: Forget that forgetful old hag, she can't even remember...that she's a hag!
Panther Thug: Fatima's just follows doofy's every little move. We have had nothin' good to say 'bout her in ages!
Miranda: "Doofy"? Sounds like a name you'd give a cute pet...
Panther Mafioso: Whatever! She ain't here right now, so what's she gonna do?
Miranda: 5 against 1? This does not conform to the rules of the martial arts.
Panther Mafioso: Rules? How 'bout you just die, you weird witch!
Miranda: Master says that a wise one knows when to run!
Panther Thug: Boss, she's getting away!
Panther Mafioso: Don't fret. This is our territory. Get 'er!
Panther Thug: Boss, I can smell that rat. She's around here somewhere, but this is the forbbiden area...
Panther Mafioso: Forbidden my rump! That haggard hag's been pulling one over on us. Let's get 'er. Pick up the pace!
Miranda: (They're closing in...they're definitely gonna find me. Got to find a way to get outta here...eh?)
Panther Mafioso: Dig out the bottom of the trees! There's nowhere left for her to hide!
Panther Mafioso: What's the matter!?
Panther Mafioso: A-A-A-A wild beast!?
Panther Mafioso: AAAHHHH!!! What kind of monster is this!?
Panther Mafioso: We're finished! FINISHED!!!
Miranda: Hey, big black panther! Look over here!
Panther Mafioso: You...this is...
Miranda: You Beasts who think you're better than humans...seen plenty of you...
Miranda: Now lookie here, a human saving your life. That change your mind?
Miranda: ──Scram!
Miranda: I'll stall for time. Bring your lackies!
Panther Mafioso: Y-Y-You...
Miranda: If you wanna live then SCRAM!
Miranda: Wah...tougher than Master when he blows a fuse...good thing they're far away, but...
Miranda: Haha, still not looking so good for me...
Miranda: Miss Fatima!?
Fatima: ......
Miranda: ...Miss Fatima, what's going on?
Fatima: This is not your average wild beast...it's the Panther God we worship.
Fatima: This is a forbidden area, that's why it attacked you. I used my identity as the Cybin to ask for forgiveness. You're fine.
Miranda: Oh, I didn't know...
Fatima: It's okay. I won't blame you for entering the forbidden area without permission.
Fatima: Those scumbags...I'm gonna punish them to the maximum degree that the tribe allows.
Miranda: So you entered the mountain to pick a Blessing Branch?
Fatima: I thought I lost you. You're pretty good.
Fatima: You're obviously entering the competition to become the champion, yet you risk your life for your enemies. I don't know what to make of you...
Miranda: Oh, haha...that...
Miranda: ....cuz I can do it.
Fatima: What do you mean?
Miranda: Whatever this power that resides can do,
Miranda: no matter how preposterous or insane, I want to try. Because I can, simple as that. The more people that can see, the better.
Fatima: You...
Miranda: ...I once knew someone...who made me want to do this.
